[文件:183-192] 🟠P1
**`newRels` 是无效计算，逻辑分支完全未生效（死代码）**
```javascript
const newRels = relationships
  .filter(r => r.target && r.type)
  .map(r => ({
    from: character?.name && !relationships.find(
      (nr) => nr.key === r.key && nr.target === character.name
    ) ? character.name : values.name,
    to: r.target,
    type: r.type,
    strength: r.strength,
    development: character?.name ? undefined : [
      { chapter: 1, event: '初遇', strength: r.strength },
    ],
  }))

// ← newRels 立即被下面的 finalRels 覆盖，完全没用到
const finalRels = newRels.map(r => ({
  from: character?.name || values.name,
  ...
}))
```
建议删除 `newRels` 相关逻辑，直接保留 `finalRels`。

---

[文件:176-180] 🟠P1
**重命名角色时过滤旧关系的条件写反了**
```javascript
if (character?.name) {
  relData.relationships = (relData.relationships || []).filter(
    r => r.from !== values.name && r.to !== values.name  // ← 用新名过滤，永远匹配不到
  )
}
```
此时 `values.name` 已经是新名字，`character.name` 才是旧名字。过滤条件写反了，应该用旧名过滤：
```javascript
r => r.from !== character.name && r.to !== character.name
```

---

[文件:82-86] 🟡P2
**`useEffect` 依赖数组不完整，`loadRelationships` 未列入**
```javascript
useEffect(() => {
  if (visible && character && projectRoot) {
    loadRelationships()
  }
}, [visible, character, projectRoot])  // ← loadRelationships 缺失
```
每次渲染 `loadRelationships` 是新引用，建议加入依赖数组或用 `useCallback` 包裹，否则 effect 行为不稳定。

---

[文件:137-140] 🟡P2
**`character?.name` 在 `character` 可能为 `null` 时被多次使用**
```javascript
const rels = (relData.relationships || []).filter(
  r => r.from === character?.name || r.to === character?.name
)
// ← 若上方 `if (visible && character && projectRoot)` 未匹配，这里 `character` 仍可能为 null
```
```javascript
// 修复：在 filter 前先断言
const charName = character?.name ?? ''
const rels = (relData.relationships || []).filter(
  r => r.from === charName || r.to === charName
)
```
